    "description": "与我们的四条腿的朋友在一起的时间是有趣和宝贵的--毫无疑问。另一方面，公寓装修和清理不守规矩的小狗造成的混乱......不是那么回事。幸运的是，只要你潜入《翻转吧！宠物》的世界，所有这些活动都会变得很有趣<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/53f78689b3560051db96b66d45444c53.poster.avif?t=1729502321\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/53f78689b3560051db96b66d45444c53.webm?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/53f78689b3560051db96b66d45444c53.mp4?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>体验独特的Furniballs游戏机制，将公寓装修和布置的过程变成像抛球一样简单的快乐游戏。定制墙壁、地板和家具，使公寓变得漂亮和舒适，并与你的四条腿的同伴一起享受它们。你的进度越快，就会有更多的公寓、家具、墙纸、装饰品和其他材料可用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/f764de380ea4b522185016a0240139e7.poster.avif?t=1729502321\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/f764de380ea4b522185016a0240139e7.webm?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/f764de380ea4b522185016a0240139e7.mp4?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>对宠物和它们可能造成的麻烦负责。打扫卫生，收集垃圾，清除污渍，修复损坏的家具，更换墙纸。也不要忘记那些可爱的生物的需求。给它们喂食，并在它们之后打扫卫生。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/884ca8cb66c03f0bb394b324674062e8.poster.avif?t=1729502321\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/884ca8cb66c03f0bb394b324674062e8.webm?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/884ca8cb66c03f0bb394b324674062e8.mp4?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与宠物一起度过美好时光。扔球给他们，和他们一起拉绳子，抚摸他们，教他们捡东西和各种新技巧。让他们开心!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/d1970026c212c23ebd0d29ccc45f0562.poster.avif?t=1729502321\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/d1970026c212c23ebd0d29ccc45f0562.webm?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839190/extras/d1970026c212c23ebd0d29ccc45f0562.mp4?t=1729502321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>还有什么能比你的爱和关注更让虚拟宠物开心的吗？有一件事--来自你和你的朋友的爱和关注! 在在线合作模式中一起享受所有的游戏内容。赋予这些公寓新的生命，训练宠物并与它们一起玩耍。",
